data.description: This well-maintained home is located on a cul-de-sac and features 3-sided brick exterior, architectural shingled roof (2017), gutters, a covered back patio and a large back yard with no rear neighbors. Inside you will find an open floor plan with new smoke/carbon monoxide detectors, high ceilings, walk-in kitchen pantry, gas cook top, and a large laundry room. The primary suite is spacious with the bathroom featuring dual sinks, standing shower, separate jetted tub and an enormous closet. Staying with the home is the refrigerator, Ring doorbell, solar screens, and a water softening system. Low taxes, city water, highly ranked schools and just minutes from Lake Conroe, Grand Park Central, Margaritaville, and The Woodlands. NEVER FLOODED. Call today!
